# Right Hand — Build Plan

## How to Read This Plan

Each sprint ends with something **runnable and testable** — never a half-built abstraction. The hard parts are marked 🔴 (slow down, understand deeply). The fast parts are marked 🟢 (follow patterns, move on). Every sprint ends with an **Architecture Checkpoint** — a question you should be able to answer before moving forward.

